4:57:32.000Z","msg":"或者幫支那解體都有好出路"},{"pid":"7ea6012227a6900adb90116671ca1337f8f9aad5","tid":1820531,"uid":187201,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T14:59:12.000Z","msg":"有生之年見到香港獨立我此生無憾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"824f68029d67e3c2fb2bec8b3deed7afb0cc147d","tid":1820531,"uid":882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T15:00:17.000Z","msg":"好想有人講一句<br />\n<br />\n年輕人你就是最美的風景"},{"pid":"19405177d000fb2099df94ccbe0b40dbfe495926","tid":1820531,"uid":67896,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T15:00:27.000Z","msg":"自己諗好點革命先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一日唔推翻依個政權<br />\n天琦一日都只會係政治犯 唔會有被選舉權<br />\n直到有我地建立到新政制<br />\n先有可能恢復到天琦嘅公民權利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99179f57b5da82013bdfa481f755f7d378f7e251","tid":1820531,"uid":294199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T15:00:47.000Z","msg":"香港要行得好<br />\n難聽都要講句搵個好聰明既世界仔做特首<br />\n唔可以盡奶共，但個心又要企香港人咁先有歌仔唱<br />\n假切一上任就「講獨」<br />\n唔計專打自己人既老解，果三萬黑警你估會企邊？<br />\n到時一係全民勇武打過，但大家心知無可能<br />\n<br />\n所以係我心目中，獨唔獨都好<br />\n都要「先」令香港變成一個有利用價值既地區<br />\n咁英美台其他國家先會更出力幫<br />\n中共都會因為咁而手軟,甚至有同佢議價能力<br />\n<br />\n所以天琦做到都好<br />\n都好睇佢取向"},{"pid":"2445551559d809521e4fe8cd37a5489153a9b024","tid":1820531,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T15:26:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"525f388c3643aa89b79a3d36f02f7af5ae5d09a1","tid":1820531,"uid":2638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdf7d379397de369f0fad8fb006b2fa356810b05","tid":1820531,"uid":293227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T14:28:04.000Z","msg":"我此生無憾<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港獨立，唯一出路"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T15:27:32.000